{
  "stem": "543.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we knew that there was concentration-- that they-- listen, if the razzias, the people were sent out, you heard about they went to camps and it was very bad.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they talked about killings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But who would believe it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we did try when-- the war started in 1940, when Germany came in and you heard about and first they came to Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then you were already on-- then they came to Holland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were already on the march then, and we know how much razzias were there for Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They picked them up, and they sent them away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was already very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I lived in Haamstede still, and we know that the war started in 1940-- and we-- when I stayed in Haamstede in my garden, I saw-- I heard and saw the people flying over the Rotterdam and that-- that they captured Holland, you know, they came-- the Germans came in Holland.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he made Rotterdam nearly flat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They bombarded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Holland is very small.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's not a big country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's populated, but it's not-- small.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the Germans came in, and we were very, very sad for sure, that-- What happened when they came in?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What did you see?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we know that-- that-- that-- that-- was bombarded-- the bombarded.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and the Dutch government, like the queen and her-- her cabinet and everybody, her people, they fled to England.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Holland was basically without, without a head of state, nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when Germans came in Holland, they took over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they started-- like the laws were already in Germany-- they came to in Holland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like you had to wear a star, that you have to give your radio in, that you can't go shopping after five o'clock.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
